name: SGLT2i
title: SGLT2i
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Medications containing SLGT2 inhibitors.),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: PHARMACOLOGIC:),(Inclusion Criteria: RxCUIs for medications containing any of the following ingredients:
* bexaglifloxin
* canagliflozin
* dapagliflozin
* empagliflozin
* ertugliflozin),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
